                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3zp3wm0j/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>Israelites <hi rend=\"underline\">generally</hi>, 'altho with some\n                                        of<lb/> the straggling followers of the now<lb/> dethroned\n                                                  <persName>Posnanski</persName>\n                                        dissatisfaction<lb/> may be created</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Of course this (the <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                                        >good</hi>,) is not the object, but<lb/> I for one will not\n                                        object if it prove an<lb/>\n                                        <hi rend=\"underline\">incident</hi> to the publications\n                                        referred<lb/> to.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have to return you the regards<lb/> &amp; good\n                                        wishes of the individuals,<lb/> to whom you desired\n                                        remembrance<lb/> &amp; subscribe myself</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Yrs Truly &amp;c</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Thos J Moise</persName>\n                              </p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
